(group funds, Pounds 175bn)
Number of UK private clients: Nearly 3,000
Number of expatriate/foreign national private clients: 165
Minimum investment for private clients: Pounds 100,000
Current asset allocation for private clients: UK equities, 58%; overseas
equities, 34%; bonds and cash, 8%
Average annual portfolio turnover: 25%
Fees: 1% a year on portfolios up to Pounds 250,000; 0.45% on the next
Pounds 750,000; 0.3% on any balance over Pounds 1m. Plus commission
charges. Minimum management fee: Pounds 1,000 a year
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
