<TEXT>
Johannesburg was hurt by a firmer financial rand, losses for South African
shares listed in New York and gold's inability to push above current levels.
The overall index lost 56 to 5,860, industrials dropped 59 to 6,603 and
golds slipped 26 to 2,269.
